text: Karlo Čović (born 9 August 1945) is a Serbian wrestler. He competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics and the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Living people Category:Serbian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Yugoslavia Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Subotica
